# OpenRouter API Configuration
# Get a free API key at: https://openrouter.ai
# 1. Visit https://openrouter.ai
# 2. Sign up for a free account
# 3. Go to dashboard and create an API key
# 4. Copy the key and paste it below

OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-your-api-key-here

# Optional: Choose a different model (default: gpt-4o-mini)
# Other options: gpt-4o, mistral-large-2407, claude-opus-4, etc.
OPENROUTER_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# Note: The system will work in DEMO MODE if no valid API key is provided.
# In demo mode, the system will:
# - Use pattern matching for drug extraction (instead of LLM)
# - Return template responses for interactions
# - Still work with database lookups
